  wordCount: 725
};

const content = `<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Step into any winning program’s <strong>locker room</strong> and you’ll feel it: the grit, the pride, the discipline. But behind that energy is something often overlooked — the <strong>sports lockers</strong> that anchor the space. Coaches know that when gear, uniforms, and personal items are organized in durable, well-designed <strong>wood lockers</strong>, the entire team operates smoother. Here’s why custom lockers are more than just storage — they’re a coaching tool.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-p-problem-the-hidden-headache-of-disorganized-locker-rooms">P – Problem: The Hidden Headache of Disorganized Locker Rooms</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Every coach has seen it. Piles of gear on the floor. Missing cleats before practice. Players wandering around trying to find their helmets. Without the right <strong>sports lockers</strong>, the locker room becomes a distraction instead of a launchpad for performance. And let’s be real — no coach wants to waste energy managing clutter when they should be building culture.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-o-opportunity-lockers-that-work-as-hard-as-the-team">O – Opportunity: Lockers That Work as Hard as the Team</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>When you upgrade to <strong>custom wood lockers</strong>, you’re not just buying furniture — you’re creating order, efficiency, and pride. Customizable <strong>lockers for sale</strong> today aren’t one-size-fits-all. They’re built to fit your team’s needs, whether that’s ventilated compartments, secure lock boxes, or even personalized name plates that make each player feel like a pro.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Coaches love them because they make management easier:</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Gear has a home.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Clean-up is faster.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Players respect the space.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>And let’s be honest — they look badass, too.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-s-solution-function-meets-grit">S – Solution: Function Meets Grit</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Here’s how custom <strong>sports lockers</strong> bring real value to every team and every coach:</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list {"ordered":true} -->
<ol class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
